<br>
I am a level 22 mage (almost 23), who should be reaching the 24th level relatively soon. I have been using the search function on this site, and had a question or two I just wanted to clear up.<br>
<br>
1) I see from my reading that it seems that I should give the weapons to the pet first, (primary, then secondary for dual wielding). Then give the armor bits piece by piece so each is equipped in its proper slot. Am I correct in this assumption? Or does it matter when I give the pieces?<br>
<br>
2) Focus items that I can summon...should I give a set to the pet in place of some of the armor? I have been reading conflicting reports and not quite sure if it is worth it or not.<br>
<br>
Thank you for your time...<br>
<br>
